            <title>[KAFKA-10079] Improve thread-level stickiness of stateful tasks</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/KAFKA-10079</link>
                <project id="12311720" key="KAFKA">Kafka</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Now that &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/KAFKA-9501&quot; title=&quot;Promote Standby tasks to active tasks without closing them&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;KAFKA-9501&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;KAFKA-9501&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; is fixed, we should make sure that KIP-441 will work with in-memory stores.&lt;/p&gt;

